dataIdInfo.idPurp: Definition for Land - As viewed from an overhead aeroplane (i.e. what you will see on Google Earth). Where precise land elevation is available, land is defined as being 2.515m above the Chart Datum (or High Water Mark) This dataset is based on various source data, including project topographic & bathymetry survey data, satellite imagery & quicklooks, and Google Earth Pro. See "lineage" for update details.
dataIdInfo.idAbs:
Definition for Land

  • As viewed from an overhead aeroplane (i.e. what you will see on Google Earth).

  • Where precise land elevation is available, land is defined as being 2.515m above the Chart Datum (or High Water Mark)

This dataset is based on various source data, including project topographic & bathymetry survey data, satellite imagery & quicklooks, and Google Earth Pro.

See "lineage" for update details.

attrdomv.udom: Sequential unique whole numbers that are automatically generated.

dataLineage.statement:
Latest below.
20100409 - Data created and QC checked by Modelling team - Northern coastline of mainland Singapore - following Spot 5 10m 20030519 satellite image (at 1:10,000 scale). Basically traced the seaward limit of the land (does not take into account the tidal height) - Tuas View and TVE - following the presumed existing coastline in SG5284 TPPPlan171.dwg (at 1:1,000 scale) as it is the best data we have for that area. - Jurong Island - following the WorldView 0.5m Oct 2009 satellite image purchased for SG5308 (at 1:5,000 scale). Not too sure about the sandy, no seawall areas on the western side. Basically traced the seaward limit of the land (does not take into account the tidal height) The rest of the shoreline has not been checked yet.
20100426 - Tekong area D updated based on SG5300 Progress Chart Mar 2010, and PPT Phase 3&4 and Changi Finger updated based on Bathy 20100424.
20100608 - Tekong Area D updated based on sketch from contractor found in: \\draco\GIS\Template\Data_Working\Shoreline\Working Files - NOT for non-GIS Team use\Existing_SG\20100607\SG7506_P.Tekong_r.img. Update by GIS intern, Jiawei.
20100803 - The following updates were made by PCF: - SG5300 Spot 2008 Jun IKONOS image used to refine P. Unum and associated reclamation area, and Area A, and mangrove area within P. Tekong. The data appeared shifted during last update in Jun. - Tekong Area B3 and Area D updated using SG5300 30 Jun 2010 Bathy/Topo survey data, where z > 2.515. - Marina South area refined using Google Earth Pro 20091102 image. - ICT area updated using SG5500 20100701 sand bund drawing - PPT Phase 3 & 4 reclamation area updated using DHI Bathy Ban D 20100730, and refined using Worldview 2 20100530 satellite quicklook.
20100907 - The following updates were made by PCF (Where SVY21 or precise coordinates were not provided, Google Earth Pro was used to derived coordinates): - Tekong area: Sandfill areas > 2.515m CD based on 20100802 topo data from EMMP Contractor - TVE: Highest resolution Worldview 1 quicklook for 20100910 - PPT to Marina South: Highest resolution Worldview 1 quicklook for 20100813 - ICT: 970.45m current training wall and piled deck (between CTW and Marina South Jetty) based on info from VHA and EMMP Contractor (PTMJV-ICT-TRW-GEN-123l(30 Aug).pdf) - P. Punggol Barat and Timor: Highest resolution Worldview 1 quicklook for 20090314 - Coney Island: Highest resolution Worldview 1 quicklook for 20100813
20100927 - Shoreline at Meranti, Jurong Island refined based on WV01 20100910 quicklook and SG5327 CAD from Client of proposed SLNG boundary.
20101005 - The following updates were made: - SG5201 PPT Reclamation - Update based on a combination of BanD 20101001, WV01 Quicklook 20100929, and Contractor's weekly work schedule 20100923. Apparent discrepancy between BanD and WV01 verified with YEO - SG5500 ICT Reclamation - Update based on WV02 20100914, and ICT Bathy data 20100918. Verification of data with YEO - SG5300 Area D Eastern Bund profile - Update on SG5300 bathy data to 20101001, SG5300 project status chart as of 20100921, and WV02 20100914. - SG5300/SG5550 - Update of rest of Tekong island using WV02 20100914. - TVE - WV01 Quicklook 20100912 - Others - General refinement of shoreline, addition of bridges
20101007 - Tekong Area D and D1 updated using SG5300 Progress Chart for Bund Level (20100920) and WV02 20100914.
20101015 - Labrador shoreline refined using highest resolution WV1 20100929 quicklook
20101122 - The following updates were made: - SG5300 Area D Eastern Bund profile - Update based on email info from Contractor on 14 Nov. No progress chart, full bathy/topo survey, or satellite imagery for verification. - SG5500 ICT Reclamation - Highest resolution quicklook for WV1 20101119 - SG5200 PPT Reclamation - Highest resolution quicklook for WV1 20101119 - SG5450 Ayer Chawan Reclamation & general refinement for Jurong Island - Highest resolution quicklook for WV2 20101119 - Tuas View Extension - Highest resolution quicklook for WV2 20101119 - P. Punggol reservoir - Highest resolution quicklook for WV1 20101016
20101210 - Seaward limit of TVE and Jurong Island reclaimed land / seawall areas that were known to exist since Joint Study (2004) was corrected using Depthlines_SDS_050104.dwg. This drawing was provided by the Singapore Government during the Joint Study as the official seaward limit for reclamation at TVE and Jurong Island. Projection was assumed SVY21. - 2.515mCD limit for current Jurong Island seawall areas were corrected against SG5342_CAD_ProJRCJetty.dwg. Projection was assumed SVY21. - Raffles Marina and 2nd link seawall / land / bridge areas refined using GEPro imagery (date Oct 200921). Raffles Marina land area corrected, as this was a glaring omission for SG5351, which involves surveys near the marina. - No edits for other parts of the island yet.
20101229 - Tekong Area D - Verified against SG5300 Progress Chart for end Dec 2010 (SVY21). No change in land profile. - Sentosa Cove, Sentosa - Updated based on SG5360 Parcellation drawing from Client (SVY21) - Southern Waterway, Sentosa - Updated based on Google Earth Pro 20090314 image, rectified based on GEPro coordinates, and corrected to fit with SG5360 Parcellation drawing - Tg. Pagar Terminal - Land extent corrected based on bathy survey extent for SG5500 TPT survey dated 20101201. - Brani Terminal - Updated based on Google Earth Pro 20090314 image, rectified based on GEPro coordinates, and corrected to fit with SG5360 Parcellation drawing - PPT Phase 3 & 4 Reclamation - Updated based on areas > 2.515m CD from SG5200 Bathymetry survey dated 20101224. - Sultan Shoal - Updated based on Google Earth Pro undated image. - Rectification based on GEPro coordinates, and checked against MPA ENC data for jetty structures.
20110221 - SG5281 drawing of Marina East shoreline - SG5300 drawing - Sand bund level progress chart - 20110221 - SG5339 drawing of reclamation profile, seawall completed 75% from NW end (info from NCH) - SG5500 bathy survey data of Tanjong Pagar Terminal - dated 20110107 - SG5500 reclamation profile drawing - dated 20110201 - SG5500 sand bund topo drawing - dated 20100701 - Satellite quicklooks - dated 201102 - for general refinement at various areas including TVE, Sisters' Island, Brani, Khatib Bongsu, Changi Finger area. - Rectification based on GEPro coordinates, and checked against MPA ENC data for jetty structures.
20110427 ======== TVE & JI - No change based on WV02 20110408 Southern Islands - No change based on WV02 20110408 Update of PPT Phase 3 & 4 reclamation area - SG5200 bathy data 20110421 Sentosa Boardwalk - SG5254 CAD drawing Keppel Harbour refined - MPA ENC 201010 Serangoon river refinement - WV02 20110408 Ubin Sg. Maman & Sg. Besar river mouth - SG5030 Aerial photo of Ubin (feedback from Anna) Tekong Area A & B - WV01 20110417 (some areas cutter dredged; confirmed by HJX) Tekong Area D - WV01 20110417, SG5300 progress chart as of 20110418 (drawing incorrect; HJX clarified limit of sand bund > 2.515 in western profile to chainage 189). Bund extended to 191 based on verbal update from HJX on 20110427. Sand bund width verified against SG5300 bathy data (combined as of 20110426) Tekong Area D1 - SG5300 bathy data (combined as of 20110131)
20110511 ======== Refine of Sg. Buloh / Kranji reservoir area using: 1) SG5317 Corridor A data from NParks 2) SG5202 Worldview 1 satellite image dated 20100414 (not security cleared) 3) MINDEF 1:50,000 Topo Map version 2006 4) Highest resolution WV02 quicklook dated 20110408
20110629 ======== Pasir Panjang Terminal Expansion Phase 3 & 4 - SG5200 Bathy Survey dated 20110624, >2.515mCD Tekong - SG5300 Bathy Survey for Areas A & B dated 20110430, > 2.515mCD; SG5300Bathy Survey for Area D dated 20110610, > 2.515mCD; SG5300 Contractor's Area D Bund level drawing (confirmed with HJX) Marina Coastal Expressway - Completed seawall based on rectified drawing from SG5339 (Info from NCH: seawall was completed as of Feb, but the contractor did not inform us until May) ICT - SG5500 Bathy survey data dated 20110624 Sg. Mandai & Sembawang Port - Refine shoreline based on WV1 quicklook dated 20110504 TVE and Jurong Island - Updated reclamation areas based on WV02 quicklook dated 20110602.
Double-checked seaward limit of TVE and Jurong Island - SG5028 Depthlines_SDS_050104.dwg. This drawing was provided by the Singapore Government during the Joint Study as the official seaward limit for reclamation at TVE and Jurong Island. Projection was assumed SVY21. - SG5342. SG5342_CAD_ProJRCJetty.dwg for recent seawall areas. Projection was assumed SVY21.
20110727 ======== - Changi East - Refined using SG5650 drawing "TJPUT-ENG-CEF-002-01" - P. Tekong Area B - Reclaimed area refined using SG5300 bathy survey dated 20110131.
20110810 ======== - Tuas - Editing artefact removed - Changi Beach - Sand flat removed
20110812 ======== - P. Tekong Area B & D - Reclaimed area refined using SG5300 bathy survey dated 20110708 and 20110805.
20110818 ======== - P. Tekong Area D (SG5300): Bathymetry survey data of Dredging and Sand Removal for Surcharge Bund in Western Bund. Updated based on the data of survey carried out at Pulau Tekong site between 12 Jul 11 to 02 Aug 11. - PPT Phase 3 and 4 Reclaimed area: updated based on the data of SG5200 bathy survey dated 20110701, 20110708, 20110715, 20110722, 20110729, 20110805, 20110812, and 20110805. - SG5201 PPT Reclamation: updated based on the bathy survey data 7th 3mth Area 1 April11, 4th 6mth Area 3 21to22 Jun11, 1st 3 mth Area G4 24,27,28 Jun & 4 July 11_v01, and 2nd 3mth Area EKF 17to18 Jun11 - SG5500 ICT Reclamation - Update based on ICT Bathy data dated 20110701, 20110708, 20110715, 20110722, 20110729, 20110815, and 20110812.
